OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782310727
OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after alleged
OL,4,Clate-night assault outside bar
OL,6,FJersey Police want to identify two men
OL,7,Fafter an alleged late-night assault in
OL,8,FSt Helier left another man needing
OL,9,Fhospital treatment.
OL,11,FThe incident happened outside The
OL,12,FBacchus Bar, near the junction of St
OL,13,FJames Street and St Saviour's Road, in
OL,14,Fthe early hours of Saturday 20 June -
OL,15,Fbetween 3:30am and 4:30am.
OL,17,FThe alleged victim was reportedly
OL,18,Fpunched and kicked by the two men,
OL,19,Fleaving him with swelling and bruising
OL,20,Fto his face, nose and body.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
