OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782310727
OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after alleged
OL,4,Clate-night assault outside bar
OL,6,FThe suspects are described as both
OL,7,Fbeing roughly six feet tall with
OL,8,Fblonde hair - one spoke with an
OL,9,FEnglish accent and the other had an
OL,10,FIrish accent.
OL,12,FThe first man is said to have been
OL,13,Fshirtless, wearing beige shorts and
OL,14,Fcarrying a black rucksack.
OL,16,FThe other is believed to have been
OL,17,Fwearing a white jacket and black
OL,18,Fshorts.
