OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1782310727
OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after alleged
OL,4,Clate-night assault outside bar
OL,6,FAnyone who witnessed the incident,
OL,7,Frecognises the men from these
OL,8,Fdescriptions, or has any other
OL,9,Finformation which may be useful, is
OL,10,Fasked to come forward.
OL,12,FThe States of Jersey Police can be
OL,13,Fcontacted on 01534 612612, or details
OL,14,Fcan be reported anonymously to the
OL,15,Fcharity Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111.
